<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṭṭut tēvatāṉam tiruccuriyal cuntarapāṇṭiya Īccuvarattu tēvarkku
<lb n="3"/>Aḷaṟṟunāṭṭu kalicalmaṅkalattut taccaṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṉ Ulakaṉēṉ veṇpunāṭṭup pi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>rammatēyam vāṉavaṉ mātēvi cavaikku <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> m <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>Aṭṭiṉamaiyil Attāṇikaḷōṭu tirutti vaicca Āṭu Irupatu
<lb n="6"/>Añcu caṭaiyaṉappi koṇṭāṉ panniraṇṭarai, nāṭaṉ panniraṇṭarai, Ivvi
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ruvarum Oruvarkkoruvar puṇai, Attāṇikaḷ vaccatu 
